ClaimDiagnosisId__c.description: ID of the diagnosis from the claim that this record is related to.

ClaimProcedureId__c.description: ID of the procedure from this claim that this record is related to.

Name__c.description: Name of the claim diagnosis procedure record.

SequenceNumber__c.description: Diagnosis sequence for the claim line item indicating whether diagnosis is primary, secondary, tertiary, and so on.

SourceSystem__c.description: An identifier of the system where this record was sourced from.

SourceSystemIdentifier__c.description: Name of the system where this record was sourced from.

SourceSystemModified__c.description: Timestamp of the most recent update from the source system
